243
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:25,280
All right?

244
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:27,240
Yes, if it's possible.

245
00:12:27,980 --> 00:12:29,340
Leave it to me.

246
00:12:29,340 --> 00:12:30,000
I have a good idea.

247
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:31,720
Wash your head and wait.

248
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,000
Hey, you!

249
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:41,140
I need a sacrifice to make a fool of you.

250
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,120
