258
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,700
You're trying to fight back the feelings that have been with you for many years.

259
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:10,180
That's right.

260
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:23,460
You can't let a regular store like this be accepted by a gourmet critic.

261
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:27,020
You can't let a regular store like this be accepted by a gourmet critic.

262
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:28,620
My store...

263
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,540
