267
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:41,340
Next...

268
00:13:48,100 --> 00:13:50,460
Hey, Ryo! What are you doing?

269
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:51,420
Hey, Ryo! What are you doing?

270
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:51,740
Hey, I'm here at a good place.

271
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:55,400
I remember you saying you made some rice balls during the school's school lunch break.

